(645, 2, 'admin/consultations/3', 'PUT', '127.0.0.1', '{\"nomConsultation\":\"Safari 1 consultation\",\"malade_id\":\"4\",\"dateCons\":\"2022-07-18\",\"resultat\":\"<p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\\\">On rencontre des patients souffrant de maladies ou de troubles psychiques ou de comportements perturb\\u00e9s dans de nombreux contextes cliniques, y compris dans les services d&#39;urgences et de m\\u00e9decine g\\u00e9n\\u00e9rale. Les maladies ou les troubles peuvent \\u00eatre nouveaux ou se placer dans la continuit\\u00e9 de troubles mentaux connus. Les plaintes peuvent \\u00eatre li\\u00e9es \\u00e0 l&#39;adaptation \\u00e0 une maladie physique ou \\u00eatre l&#39;effet direct d&#39;une maladie physique sur le cerveau. La m\\u00e9thode de diagnostic d\\u00e9pend du contexte; soit les plaintes exprim\\u00e9es constituent une urgence, soit elles sont rapport\\u00e9es lors d&#39;une consultation programm\\u00e9e. En cas d&#39;urgence, le m\\u00e9decin doit se concentrer sur l&#39;anamn\\u00e8se r\\u00e9cente, la symptomatologie et le comportement pour prendre une d\\u00e9cision. Lors d&#39;une consultation programm\\u00e9e, une \\u00e9valuation plus compl\\u00e8te est n\\u00e9cessaire.<\\/p><p><span id=\\\"v36188007_fr\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Fallback, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\\\">L&#39;\\u00e9valuation m\\u00e9dicale des patients qui pr\\u00e9sentent des troubles mentaux cherche \\u00e0 identifier 3 choses:<\\/p><ul data-mmanualobjecttype=\\\"List\\\" class=\\\"bulleted list-paddingleft-2\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none;\\\"><li><p><span id=\\\"v1024642_fr\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute;\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em; display: inline;\\\">Les troubles physiques&nbsp;<em style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none;\\\">ressemblant<\\/em>&nbsp;\\u00e0 des troubles psychiatriques<\\/p><\\/li><li><p><span id=\\\"v7539890_fr\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute;\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em; display: inline;\\\">Les troubles physiques&nbsp;<em style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none;\\\">provoqu\\u00e9s par<\\/em>&nbsp;des troubles psychiatriques ou leur traitement<\\/p><\\/li><li><p><span id=\\\"v1024644_fr\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute;\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em; display: inline;\\\">Les troubles somatiques&nbsp;<em style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none;\\\">accompagnant<\\/em>&nbsp;des troubles psychiatriques<\\/p><\\/li><\\/ul><p><span id=\\\"v1024645_fr\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Fallback, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\\\">De nombreux troubles physiques entra\\u00eenent des sympt\\u00f4mes identiques \\u00e0 des troubles psychiatriques sp\\u00e9cifiques (voir tableau&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-psychiatriques\\/prise-en-charge-du-patient-pr%C3%A9sentant-des-troubles-mentaux\\/%C3%A9valuation-m%C3%A9dicale-du-patient-pr%C3%A9sentant-des-troubles-mentaux#v1024672_fr\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Sympt\\u00f4mes mentaux dus \\u00e0 des troubles physiques\\\" data-id=\\\"b200565f-7795-4f88-adec-95c32df8b43f\\\" data-itemid=\\\"72148782-2cd7-4456-b2e0-3fef013b0460\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">Sympt\\u00f4mes mentaux dus \\u00e0 des troubles physiques<\\/a>). D&#39;autres troubles physiques peuvent ne pas ressembler \\u00e0 des syndromes mentaux sp\\u00e9cifiques, mais entra\\u00eenent plut\\u00f4t une modification de l&#39;humeur et de l&#39;\\u00e9nergie.<\\/p><p><span id=\\\"v1024647_fr\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Fallback, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\\\">De nombreux m\\u00e9dicaments provoquent des troubles psychiatriques; les classes de causes m\\u00e9dicamenteuses les plus fr\\u00e9quentes sont<\\/p><ul data-mmanualobjecttype=\\\"List\\\" class=\\\"bulleted list-paddingleft-2\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none;\\\"><li><p><span id=\\\"v1024650_fr\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute;\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em; display: inline;\\\">M\\u00e9dicaments actifs sur le syst\\u00e8me nerveux central (p. ex.,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-neurologiques\\/troubles-convulsifs\\/traitement-m%C3%A9dicamenteux-des-convulsions\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Traitement m\\u00e9dicamenteux des convulsions\\\" data-id=\\\"dfa4f009-3001-4a3e-92c7-6c4c2aba26e8\\\" data-itemid=\\\"0ae688a6-77c3-47ea-bd28-a3f6a3e29ebd\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">anticonvulsivants<\\/a>,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-psychiatriques\\/troubles-de-l-humeur\\/traitement-pharmacologique-de-la-d%C3%A9pression\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Traitement pharmacologique de la d\\u00e9pression\\\" data-id=\\\"4624f742-b306-482d-8fbf-7e18ea904632\\\" data-itemid=\\\"5d081893-367f-42f3-ac7d-4e6a0a9ec84b\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">antid\\u00e9presseurs<\\/a>,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-psychiatriques\\/schizophr%C3%A9nie-et-troubles-apparent%C3%A9s\\/schizophr%C3%A9nie#v1029264_fr\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Traitement\\\" data-id=\\\"798a97e9-ee77-446d-9f3c-c214de131fec\\\" data-itemid=\\\"c5112948-45db-4544-aa3b-9f8aab88ab55\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">antipsychotiques<\\/a>,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/sujets-sp%C3%A9ciaux\\/drogues-et-substances-intoxicantes-%C3%A0-usage-r%C3%A9cr%C3%A9atif\\/anxiolytiques-et-s%C3%A9datifs\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Anxiolytiques et s\\u00e9datifs\\\" data-id=\\\"85d97598-753f-44a1-9e49-ccb967ba0724\\\" data-itemid=\\\"87eab328-f84a-4a99-8ad0-e86d7cb42374\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">s\\u00e9datifs\\/hypnotiques<\\/a>, stimulants)<\\/p><\\/li><li><p><span id=\\\"v1024652_fr\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute;\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em; display: inline;\\\">Anticholinergiques (p. ex., antihistaminiques)<\\/p><\\/li><li><p><span id=\\\"v1024654_fr\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute;\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em; display: inline;\\\">Corticost\\u00e9ro\\u00efdes<\\/p><\\/li><\\/ul><p><span id=\\\"v1024655_fr\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Fallback, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\\\">De nombreux autres m\\u00e9dicaments et classes de m\\u00e9dicaments sont \\u00e9galement impliqu\\u00e9s; ils comprennent certaines classes qui ne sont pas prises habituellement en consid\\u00e9ration (p. ex., antibiotiques, antihypertenseurs). La prise de drogues, en particulier l&#39;&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/sujets-sp%C3%A9ciaux\\/drogues-et-substances-intoxicantes-%C3%A0-usage-r%C3%A9cr%C3%A9atif\\/intoxication-et-sevrage-alcoolique\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Intoxication et sevrage alcoolique\\\" data-id=\\\"8f15083c-2edc-414c-a6f0-bcd43a78e9be\\\" data-itemid=\\\"63f66a52-0c5d-4d03-b93f-bd45d6343606\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">alcool<\\/a>, les&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/sujets-sp%C3%A9ciaux\\/drogues-et-substances-intoxicantes-%C3%A0-usage-r%C3%A9cr%C3%A9atif\\/amph%C3%A9tamines\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Amph\\u00e9tamines\\\" data-id=\\\"08b0fbd6-4674-40cc-ad36-75172f316524\\\" data-itemid=\\\"01fbb6c8-6d1f-4b7b-ad3f-aa39dd58b125\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">amph\\u00e9tamines<\\/a>, la&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/sujets-sp%C3%A9ciaux\\/drogues-et-substances-intoxicantes-%C3%A0-usage-r%C3%A9cr%C3%A9atif\\/marijuana-cannabis\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Marijuana (Cannabis)\\\" data-id=\\\"73b7dba6-6d7c-40a4-85ba-c35d88900a6b\\\" data-itemid=\\\"b7e20cd2-729b-443f-b9aa-5c977682b63c\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">marijuana (cannabis)<\\/a>, la&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/sujets-sp%C3%A9ciaux\\/drogues-et-substances-intoxicantes-%C3%A0-usage-r%C3%A9cr%C3%A9atif\\/coca%C3%AFne\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Coca\\u00efne\\\" data-id=\\\"91da3b8c-20cc-4cc4-90d5-11e6e8074d3f\\\" data-itemid=\\\"f2e8e1ef-d88a-4c43-9394-4817ca32e5a2\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">coca\\u00efne<\\/a>, les&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/sujets-sp%C3%A9ciaux\\/drogues-et-substances-intoxicantes-%C3%A0-usage-r%C3%A9cr%C3%A9atif\\/hallucinog%C3%A8nes\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Hallucinog\\u00e8nes\\\" data-id=\\\"da029cd2-96ad-4a5a-bd7b-97884e2c9471\\\" data-itemid=\\\"7e8d55ae-9faf-452d-8615-900683564eac\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">hallucinog\\u00e8nes<\\/a>&nbsp;et la&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/sujets-sp%C3%A9ciaux\\/drogues-et-substances-intoxicantes-%C3%A0-usage-r%C3%A9cr%C3%A9atif\\/k%C3%A9tamine-et-phencyclidine-pcp\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"K\\u00e9tamine et phencyclidine (PCP)\\\" data-id=\\\"186c7f01-8c71-4743-8db4-02a99627c21a\\\" data-itemid=\\\"26564a3d-524c-470f-98c6-c64664c94d05\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">phencyclidine<\\/a>&nbsp;(PCP), en particulier en cas d&#39;overdose sont \\u00e9galement des causes fr\\u00e9quentes de sympt\\u00f4mes psychiatriques. Le sevrage de l&#39;alcool, des barbituriques ou des benzodiaz\\u00e9pines peuvent provoquer des sympt\\u00f4mes psychiatriques (p. ex., de l&#39;anxi\\u00e9t\\u00e9) en plus des sympt\\u00f4mes de sevrage physique.<\\/p><p><span id=\\\"v1024656_fr\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Fallback, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\\\">Les patients qui pr\\u00e9sentent un trouble mental peuvent d\\u00e9velopper un trouble physique sans relation (p. ex., une&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-neurologiques\\/m%C3%A9ningite\\/revue-g%C3%A9n%C3%A9rale-des-m%C3%A9ningites\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Revue g\\u00e9n\\u00e9rale des m\\u00e9ningites\\\" data-id=\\\"afeb37d5-658c-4b08-85cd-7f17ae457093\\\" data-itemid=\\\"2ae7e917-780f-4804-8b6c-779691bc4f35\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">m\\u00e9ningite<\\/a>, une&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-endocriniens-et-m%C3%A9taboliques\\/diab%C3%A8te-sucr%C3%A9-et-troubles-du-m%C3%A9tabolisme-glucidique\\/acidoc%C3%A9tose-diab%C3%A9tique\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Acidoc\\u00e9tose diab\\u00e9tique\\\" data-id=\\\"ddeb7399-8567-46f9-b35d-8e7c7d7e76e5\\\" data-itemid=\\\"d7e529e3-87f2-4974-83c4-1758ef675820\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">acidoc\\u00e9tose diab\\u00e9tique<\\/a>) qui cause de nouveaux sympt\\u00f4mes mentaux ou aggravent les existants. Ainsi, il convient de ne pas syst\\u00e9matiquement supposer que tous les sympt\\u00f4mes mentaux d&#39;un patient qui pr\\u00e9sente un trouble mental connu sont dus \\u00e0 ce trouble. Le m\\u00e9decin doit se monter proactif dans la prise en compte des causes physiques possibles des sympt\\u00f4mes mentaux, en particulier chez les patients incapables de d\\u00e9crire leur \\u00e9tat de sant\\u00e9 physique parce qu&#39;ils pr\\u00e9sentent une psychose ou une d\\u00e9mence.<\\/p><p><a id=\\\"v55480222_fr\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Fallback, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; text-decoration-line: underline; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50); font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Fallback, sans-serif; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p><span id=\\\"v36188019_fr\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none;\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><h3 class=\\\"title\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 4px; padding: 0px 0px 4px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 1.125rem; color: rgb(23, 79, 109); letter-spacing: 0.01em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(188, 188, 188);\\\">Pi\\u00e8ges \\u00e0 \\u00e9viter<\\/h3><table><tbody style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none;\\\"><tr class=\\\"odd firstRow\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none;\\\"><td style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none;\\\"><ul data-mmanualobjecttype=\\\"List\\\" class=\\\"bulleted list-paddingleft-2\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none;\\\"><li><p><span id=\\\"v66741124\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute;\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em; display: inline;\\\">Ne pas syst\\u00e9matiquement supposez que tous les sympt\\u00f4mes mentaux d&#39;un patient qui pr\\u00e9sente un trouble mental connu sont dus \\u00e0 ce trouble.<\\/p><\\/li><\\/ul><\\/td><\\/tr><\\/tbody><\\/table><p><span id=\\\"v1024657_fr\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Fallback, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\\\">Les patients se pr\\u00e9sentant pour des soins psychiatriques ont parfois des troubles physiques non diagnostiqu\\u00e9es qui ne sont pas la cause de leurs sympt\\u00f4mes mentaux mais n\\u00e9anmoins exigent un bilan et un traitement. Ces troubles peuvent \\u00eatre sans rapport (p. ex.,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-cardiovasculaires\\/hypertension-art%C3%A9rielle\\/hypertension\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Hypertension\\\" data-id=\\\"3822bde5-d604-4690-a2be-f38cce07a383\\\" data-itemid=\\\"02dc5686-2749-4f6d-b08d-541662d7619f\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">hypertension<\\/a>,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-cardiovasculaires\\/coronaropathie\\/angor\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Angor\\\" data-id=\\\"b62cc795-7aa2-4490-a35e-e241017f0798\\\" data-itemid=\\\"817fcbb6-b833-4741-8296-ae4670bb2a78\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">angine de poitrine<\\/a>) ou caus\\u00e9s par le trouble mental (p. ex.,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-nutritionnels\\/d%C3%A9nutrition\\/revue-g%C3%A9n%C3%A9rale-de-la-d%C3%A9nutrition\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Revue g\\u00e9n\\u00e9rale de la d\\u00e9nutrition\\\" data-id=\\\"e41aa3a7-a270-487e-8d83-4dfae6134636\\\" data-itemid=\\\"b99c41c4-d601-4610-864c-b41b7626fcfb\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">sous-alimentation<\\/a>&nbsp;par manque de motivation ou r\\u00e9sultant d&#39;une psychose chronique&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-psychiatriques\\/schizophr%C3%A9nie-et-troubles-apparent%C3%A9s\\/schizophr%C3%A9nie\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Schizophr\\u00e9nie\\\" data-id=\\\"637fc314-4e23-4e31-b906-0bef8f21048c\\\" data-itemid=\\\"c5112948-45db-4544-aa3b-9f8aab88ab55\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">schizophr\\u00e9nie<\\/a>) ou par son traitement (p. ex.,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-endocriniens-et-m%C3%A9taboliques\\/troubles-thyro%C3%AFdiens\\/hypothyro%C3%AFdie\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Hypothyro\\u00efdie\\\" data-id=\\\"061ae9b2-8e12-4031-bd8e-501f17759007\\\" data-itemid=\\\"4303347e-ced9-48b8-a755-c64a0f5273a7\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">hypothyro\\u00efdie<\\/a>&nbsp;due au&nbsp;<span class=\\\"disableDrug\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none;\\\">lithium<\\/span>,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-endocriniens-et-m%C3%A9taboliques\\/dyslipid%C3%A9mies\\/dyslipid%C3%A9mie\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Dyslipid\\u00e9mie\\\" data-id=\\\"bb333354-210f-4304-a87c-bfd9c73ec566\\\" data-itemid=\\\"0d8d27d1-74f5-429a-ae76-a8160fcf21a3\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">hyperlipid\\u00e9mie<\\/a>&nbsp;secondaire \\u00e0 l&#39;utilisation d&#39;antipsychotiques atypiques).<\\/p><p><br\\/><\\/p>\",\"nbrSeance\":\"4\",\"_token\":\"q0XdyLjgGzl4ieQzL6ghCBZf9d4C9l5vkpuytjXh\",\"_method\":\"PUT\",\"_previous_\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/admin\\/consultations\"}', '2022-07-19 18:46:00', '2022-07-19 18:46:00'),
