INSERT INTO `admin_operation_log` (`id`, `user_id`, `path`, `method`, `ip`, `input`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(648, 2, 'admin/consultations/4', 'PUT', '127.0.0.1', '{\"nomConsultation\":\"Justin consultation 1\",\"malade_id\":\"5\",\"dateCons\":\"2022-06-26\",\"resultat\":\"<p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\\\">Le patient qui pr\\u00e9sente des modifications importantes de l&#39;humeur, des pens\\u00e9es ou du comportement et celui qui subit les effets ind\\u00e9sirables de m\\u00e9dicaments pouvant mettre en jeu le pronostic vital, requiert une \\u00e9valuation psychiatrique et un traitement urgents. Les non sp\\u00e9cialistes constituent souvent les premiers soignants des patients hospitalis\\u00e9s ou non, mais chaque fois que possible, de tels cas doivent \\u00e9galement \\u00eatre \\u00e9valu\\u00e9s par un psychiatre.<\\/p><p><span id=\\\"v1024901_fr\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Fallback, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\\\">Lorsque l&#39;humeur, les pens\\u00e9es ou le comportement d&#39;un patient sont tr\\u00e8s inhabituels ou d\\u00e9sorganis\\u00e9s, l&#39;\\u00e9valuation doit tout d&#39;abord d\\u00e9terminer si le patient est<\\/p><ul data-mmanualobjecttype=\\\"List\\\" class=\\\"bulleted list-paddingleft-2\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none;\\\"><li><p><span id=\\\"v1024905_fr\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute;\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em; display: inline;\\\">Une menace pour lui-m\\u00eame<\\/p><\\/li><li><p><span id=\\\"v1024907_fr\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute;\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em; display: inline;\\\">Une menace pour les autres<\\/p><\\/li><\\/ul><p><span id=\\\"v1024908_fr\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Fallback, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\\\">La menace pour lui-m\\u00eame peut consister en une incapacit\\u00e9 \\u00e0 s&#39;occuper de soi (aboutissant \\u00e0 une n\\u00e9gligence de soi) ou \\u00e0 un&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-psychiatriques\\/comportement-suicidaire-et-automutilation\\/comportement-suicidaire\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Comportement suicidaire\\\" data-id=\\\"d4ced372-74d9-4377-8b23-807e03bbd05d\\\" data-itemid=\\\"f10dca43-c13c-4352-ab26-c806fe0e6dd9\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">comportement suicidaire<\\/a>. La n\\u00e9gligence de soi est particuli\\u00e8rement caract\\u00e9ristique des patients qui pr\\u00e9sentent des troubles psychotiques, une d\\u00e9mence ou un abus de substance, car leur capacit\\u00e9 \\u00e0 se procurer des aliments, des v\\u00eatements et \\u00e0 se prot\\u00e9ger convenablement de l&#39;ext\\u00e9rieur est entrav\\u00e9e.<\\/p><p><span id=\\\"v1024912_fr\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Fallback, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\\\">Les patients repr\\u00e9sentant une menace pour les autres comprennent ceux qui sont activement violents (c&#39;est-\\u00e0-dire, agression des membres du personnel, lancer et casser des objets), ceux qui semblent belliqueux et hostiles (c&#39;est-\\u00e0-dire, potentiellement violents), et ceux qui ne semblent pas menacer l&#39;examinateur et les membres du personnel mais ont la ferme l&#39;intention de nuire \\u00e0 une autre personne (p. ex., conjoint, voisin, personnage public). Il est \\u00e9galement important d&#39;identifier les aidants naturels qui ne peuvent pas en toute s\\u00e9curit\\u00e9 et de mani\\u00e8re ad\\u00e9quate prendre soin de leurs personnes \\u00e0 charge.<\\/p><p><\\/p><section id=\\\"v1024913_fr\\\" class=\\\"topic__section GHead\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Fallback, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; break-inside: avoid; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><span itemscope=\\\"\\\" itemtype=\\\"http:\\/\\/schema.org\\/MedicalCause\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none;\\\"><\\/span><h2 id=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"topic__header--section\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 12px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 1.125rem; letter-spacing: 0.18px; min-width: 1px; display: flow-root; line-height: 1.9375rem; word-break: break-word; cursor: default; border: 0px; white-space: pre-line;\\\"><span itemprop=\\\"name\\\" id=\\\"v1024914_fr\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute;\\\"><\\/span>Causes<\\/h2><p><span id=\\\"v1024915_fr\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; position: absolute;\\\"><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.375rem; letter-spacing: 0.01em;\\\">Les patients agressifs et violents sont souvent psychotiques et sont porteurs de diagnostics tels qu&#39;&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-psychiatriques\\/troubles-associ%C3%A9s-%C3%A0-la-substance\\/troubles-de-toxicomanie\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Troubles de toxicomanie\\\" data-id=\\\"78100cde-b4a0-4dcc-bf85-239f9d7ff412\\\" data-itemid=\\\"a4545c29-80b7-4497-addd-68cdb0bcd6d5\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">abus de substances<\\/a>,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-psychiatriques\\/schizophr%C3%A9nie-et-troubles-apparent%C3%A9s\\/schizophr%C3%A9nie\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Schizophr\\u00e9nie\\\" data-id=\\\"ea067778-20b0-4d3e-90f0-ef3067a8bb98\\\" data-itemid=\\\"c5112948-45db-4544-aa3b-9f8aab88ab55\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">schizophr\\u00e9nie<\\/a>,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-psychiatriques\\/schizophr%C3%A9nie-et-troubles-apparent%C3%A9s\\/trouble-psychotique-bref\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Trouble psychotique bref\\\" data-id=\\\"f66a7237-fb6e-4873-b749-c52aade62e48\\\" data-itemid=\\\"1d8b5040-93a1-49f6-a1c3-1dc7f1d1634a\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">trouble psychotique bref<\\/a>,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-psychiatriques\\/schizophr%C3%A9nie-et-troubles-apparent%C3%A9s\\/trouble-d%C3%A9lirant\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Trouble d\\u00e9lirant\\\" data-id=\\\"78015f13-ed3f-41e2-b0ca-654032667010\\\" data-itemid=\\\"0dab363f-cfe0-4935-ad22-d1e113e13081\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">trouble d\\u00e9lirant<\\/a>, ou&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-psychiatriques\\/troubles-de-l-humeur\\/troubles-bipolaires#v47623762_fr\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Manie\\\" data-id=\\\"c725fae4-ef73-4efd-8ac6-0177f4beb483\\\" data-itemid=\\\"0da326e3-b9c6-498c-9ac1-f59f54a29b6e\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">\\u00e9tat maniaque<\\/a>&nbsp;aigu. D&#39;autres causes comprennent les troubles physiques qui causent un&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-neurologiques\\/syndrome-confusionnel-et-d%C3%A9mence\\/confusion\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Confusion\\\" data-id=\\\"7f2d3f77-7ca0-4d99-9094-b1645dfabe6d\\\" data-itemid=\\\"e257b55f-1660-4b85-93f7-6918c3e8f230\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">syndrome confusionnel<\\/a>&nbsp;aigu (voir&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-psychiatriques\\/prise-en-charge-du-patient-pr%C3%A9sentant-des-troubles-mentaux\\/%C3%A9valuation-m%C3%A9dicale-du-patient-pr%C3%A9sentant-des-troubles-mentaux#v1024672_fr\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Sympt\\u00f4mes mentaux dus \\u00e0 des troubles physiques\\\" data-id=\\\"dbf614e4-ad6e-4aaa-ba32-032659c88b86\\\" data-itemid=\\\"72148782-2cd7-4456-b2e0-3fef013b0460\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">Domaines \\u00e0 \\u00e9tudier lors de l&#39;\\u00e9valuation psychiatrique initiale<\\/a>), un trouble c\\u00e9r\\u00e9bral organique chronique (p. ex., une&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/troubles-neurologiques\\/syndrome-confusionnel-et-d%C3%A9mence\\/d%C3%A9mence\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"D\\u00e9mence\\\" data-id=\\\"8760f363-8567-413f-b0aa-3dcb64491e70\\\" data-itemid=\\\"e637a15a-af7f-4ee8-895f-0bdd08e256e3\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">d\\u00e9mence<\\/a>) et l&#39;intoxication par l&#39;&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/sujets-sp%C3%A9ciaux\\/drogues-et-substances-intoxicantes-%C3%A0-usage-r%C3%A9cr%C3%A9atif\\/intoxication-et-sevrage-alcoolique\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Intoxication et sevrage alcoolique\\\" data-id=\\\"be089b81-208f-4287-b26b-fe35b49f2f0e\\\" data-itemid=\\\"63f66a52-0c5d-4d03-b93f-bd45d6343606\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">alcool<\\/a>&nbsp;ou d&#39;autres substances, en particulier la m\\u00e9thamph\\u00e9tamine, la&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/sujets-sp%C3%A9ciaux\\/drogues-et-substances-intoxicantes-%C3%A0-usage-r%C3%A9cr%C3%A9atif\\/coca%C3%AFne\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"Coca\\u00efne\\\" data-id=\\\"038b2196-7631-46d2-a72e-f333b6897d71\\\" data-itemid=\\\"f2e8e1ef-d88a-4c43-9394-4817ca32e5a2\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">coca\\u00efne<\\/a>, et parfois la&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/sujets-sp%C3%A9ciaux\\/drogues-et-substances-intoxicantes-%C3%A0-usage-r%C3%A9cr%C3%A9atif\\/k%C3%A9tamine-et-phencyclidine-pcp\\\" data-toggle=\\\"tooltip\\\" title=\\\"K\\u00e9tamine et phencyclidine (PCP)\\\" data-id=\\\"cc55e2ea-51cd-4fdc-962e-ad599a57f405\\\" data-itemid=\\\"26564a3d-524c-470f-98c6-c64664c94d05\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-size-adjust: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(177, 46, 50);\\\">phencyclidine<\\/a>&nbsp;(PCP) et les drogues festives (p. ex.,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.msdmanuals.com\\/fr\\/professional\\/sujets-sp%C3%A9ciaux\\/drogues-et-substances-intoxicantes-%C3%A0-usage-r%C3%A9cr%C3%A9atif\\/m%C3%A9thyl%C3%A8ne-dioxym